      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2; sample provenance documented in experimental protocol.",
      "rationale": "Bovine blood sample provenance and preparation protocol are documented in the FDA benchmark experimental report. Statistical characterization of sample variability is not required at MRL 2."
